erdal (risperidone)." Janssen Pharmaceutica, Titusville, NJ.[4] "Product Information. Risperdal (risperidone)." Janssen Pharmaceutica, Titusville, NJ.[5] "Product Information. Uroxatral (alfuzosin)." sanofi-aventis , Bridgewater, NJ.', 1767365203);
